title: Heidi Daus "A-Maize-Ing" Pavé Crystal Pin
description:
Heidi Daus "A-Maize-Ing" Pavé Crystal Pin
You can almost hear the crunching leaves under your feet when you wear this pretty celebration of all things autumn. Heidi Daus designed her extraordinary A-Maize-Ing pin to help you savor the season each and every year. Whether you wear it or display it in all it's glory, it'll bring a smile (and a whole lot of memories) to mind.

Design Information

  • Dimensional, corncob design with husk and silk is encrusted with pavé-set, multi-sized round crystals

Crystal Information
  • This piece contains light Colorado topaz-, light smoked topaz-, smoked topaz-, topaz-, golden shadow-, burgundy-, amethyst- and Montana-color crystals
